subSections.title: Etymology
subSections.text:
; “to make enter > to accept, to receive; to contribute”
: Causative of {{och-l|入|to enter}}, the glyph which is part of {{zh-l|*內|to be inside}}, also related.

; “nano-”
: Borrowed from {{bor|zh|en|nano-}}.
